name: '91 Series No. 1A
description: Original work by SSIM. The Series includes three still images of the ’91 Series No 1 (One of One) which is tokenized as an ERC-721 on Ethereum’s Blockchain. These stills are minted on Hicetnunc and numbered 1A, 1B & 1C. Each edition is numbered to 25. This is an abstract view of a painter from the 20th century (Year 1900-2000) who expresses his imagination on the future of space travel - To see more: www.ssimartist.com / @ssimartist
